ons assets billions                the order offers a modern professional insurance operation with more than  billion of life insurance policies in force and  billion in assets as of june update a figure more than double the  levels nearly  life certificates were issued in  almost  more than the orders closest competitor to bring the total to  million the program has a  billion surplus over  million in death benefits were paid in  and  billion were paid between  and  this is large enough to rank th on the a m best list of all life insurance companies in north america since the founding of the order  billion in death benefits have been paid premiums in  were nearly  billion and dividends paid out totaled more than  million over the same time period annuity deposits rose  compared to an  loss for the industry as a whole every day in  more than  million was invested for a total of  billion on the year and an annual income of  million the order maintains a two prong investment strategy a company must first be a sound investment before stock in it is purchased and secondly the companys activities must not conflict with catholic social teaching the order also provides mortgages to churches and catholic schools at very competitive rates through its churchloan program products include permanent and term life insurance as well as annuities long term care insurance and disability insurance the insurance program is not a separate business offered by the order to others but is exclusively for the benefit of members and their families according to the fortune  list the knights of columbus ranked  in total revenue in  and with more than  agents was th in size in  all agents are members of the ordercitation needed the orders insurance program is the most highly rated program in north america for  consecutive years the order has received a m bests highest rating a additionally the order is certified by the insurance marketplace standards association for ethical sales practices stan