e global wheelchair mission recognizing that the need was still great in haiti some seven months after the disaster the knights of columbus partnered with project medishare in august  for an initiative entitled healing haitis children the initiative backed by a more than  million commitment from the knights of columbus provides free prosthetic limbs and a minimum of two years of rehab to every child who suffered an amputation from injuries sustained during the earthquake as of update more than  children had already been aided by the program after the sandy hook elementary school shooting a local council in newtown connecticut established a program asking people to pray a minimum of three hail marys for the victims and their families over  people pledged to say  million prayers more than  was donated to hurricane sandy relief efforts and  to victims of the april  tornadoes in oklahoma after west fertilizer company explosion in texas nearly a quarter of a million dollars were raised in total more than  million were donated by individual councils for disaster relief in  insurance programedit year insurance in force billions assets billions                the order offers a modern professional insurance operation with more than  billion of life insurance policies in force and  billion in assets as of june update a figure more than double the  levels nearly  life certificates were issued in  almost  more than the orders closest competitor to bring the total to  million the program has a  billion surplus over  million in death benefits were paid in  and  billion were paid between  and  this is large enough to rank th on the a m best list of all life insurance companies in north america since the founding of the order  billion in death benefits have been paid premiums in  were nearly  billion and dividends paid out totaled more than  million over the same time period annuity deposits rose  compared to an  loss for the industry as a whole every day in  more than  million was invested for a total of  billion on the year and an annual income of  million the order maintains a two prong investment strategy a company must first be a sound investment before stock in it is purchased and secondly the companys activities must not conflict with catholic social teaching the order also provides mortgages to churches and catholic schools at very competitive rates through its churchloan program products include permanent and term life insurance as well as annuities long term care insurance and disability insurance the insurance program is not a separate business offered by the order to others but is exclusively for the benefit of members and their families according to the fortune  list the knights of columbus ranked  in total revenue in  and with more than  agents was th in size in  all agents are members of the ordercitation needed the orders insurance program is the most highly rated program in north america for  consecutive years the order has received a m bests highest rating a additionally the order is certified by the insurance marketplace standards association for ethical sales practices standard  poors downgraded the insurance programs financial strengthcredit rating from aaa to aa in august  not due to the orders financial strength but due to its lowering of the longterm sovereign credit rating of the united states to aanb  additionally the insurance program has a low  lapse rate of the  million members and their families who are insured organizationedit year membership councils                as of update there were  knights and membership has grown each year for  consecutive years each member belongs to one of  councils around the world in addition there is a round tablenb  presence in lithuania knights of columbus councils fourth degree assemblies and columbian squire circles have similar officers in the councils officer titles are prefixed with worthy while in assemblies officer titles are prefixed with faithful in addition to the col