charity unity fraternity patriotism  knights of columbus welcome to our knights of columbus online store the english company inc is family owned and operated by kofc knights we have been an established and popular company in the order with an excellent track record for best customer satisfaction we have never compromised on the quality and the services provided to the customer we believe in keeping the customers happy and providing them with products at a competent price we also take tremendous pride in being the leading designated official supplier and manufacturer for the knights of columbus in the united states order online  hours a day or by phone   am pm est mondayfriday pay with visa mastercard discover card personalcouncilassembly checks and money orders what some of our customers are saying  i recently ordered a regalia package from your company needless to say i am very satisfied with your products the sword far exceeded my expectationsit is beautifully done with outstanding craftsmanship the cape chapeau and chapeau carrying case along with the sword carrying case are all superbly made your customer service department was very kind friendly and professional while working to make to sure i was satisfied with order your customer service is second to none be assured i will always give you a big 👍🏻👍🏻 up recommendation well done english company sincerely and fraternally john s  i want to express my sincere thanks for your wonderful and expedient service wow such professional and friendly service we were surprised to get the order so fast from marvin d  just wanted to say thank you again for the beautiful plaques for the council they are perfect and look great i appreciate all the help you have given to our brother knights from bill s  as fn of our assembly it is with great pride and pleasure that we extend to you and your staff our gratitude for your prompt service to our requests for equipment we have found that it only takes one phone call and your response time is outstanding and the supplies are excellent fraternally nestor d  as master i bought all my gear through them great company and great people that work there you buy from them and you get quality thank eugene d  great company i ordered some items online and received them quicker than i thought i would i will most definitely order from them again in the future and tell all my brother knights to order from them as well thank you christopher b items on sale no   kofc mug kofc challenger mug with the emblem imprinted in metallic gold color our price  no   kofc mouse pad kofc mouse pad with the emblem of the order retail  on sale  you save  no s  kofc scarf cashmere feel scarf  blacklight grey our price  no s  kofc herringbone plaid scarf cashmere feel scarf  blackcamel our price    knight in armor glass christmas ornament knight in armor glass christmas ornament makes a nice christmas gift selling fast dont miss out retail  on sale  you save  no lt  laptop computer bag kofc laptop computer bag made by manhattan embroidered emblem of the order attached in full color retail  on sale  you save  no bk  th degree laser etched black plated steel ring th degree laser etched black plated steel ring retail  on sale  you save  no btr  kofc laser etched tungsten carbide ring k of c laser etched tungsten ring  retail  on sale  you save  no bk  kofc laser etched black plated steel ring kofc laser etched black plated steel ring retail  on sale  you save  no   kofc canvas sports watch available with emblem of the order or th degree emblem on face retail  on sale  you save  no btr  laser kofc laser etched tungsten carbide ring k of c laser etched tungsten ring  retail  on sale  you save  no ltm  kofc blue can travel mug available with emblem of the order or th degree retail  on sale  you save  nol  kofc outdoorsman shirt clearance retail  on sale  you save  nos  kofc outdoorsman shirt clearance retail  on sale  you save  no btr  kofc laser etched tungsten carbide ring k of c laser